snippet.title: Arcade Game: Tank 8 (1976 Atari) [Re-Uploaeded]
snippet.description:
A Tank battle shooting game where controls are a pain. I also noticed that tanks can only be destroyed in multiplayer mode not single player.  Not the best atari has done.

Emulator and Recorder: mameui 0.149.
Encoder: AviSynth + MeGui.

Info: Re-Uploaded for not only better video quality but also for the correct original aspect ratio.
